# Frontend Components

shadcn/ui primitives + proje-özel shared component'lar. Component reuse disiplin — paralel implementasyon yasak.

## Lean Design System ile hizalama

`docs/lean-design-system/` (token + `ls-*` sınıfları) görsel dilin kaynağıdır. shadcn primitive özelleştirirken renk, radius, shadow ve spacing **önce** `tokens.css` değişkenleriyle ifade edilir; kart/buton vb. için `components.css` içindeki `ls-*` pattern’leri README ile uyumlu kullanılır. Çatışma: README ve **`26-lean-design-system.mdc`** önceliklidir.

## Component Kategorileri

```
components/
├── ui/              # shadcn/ui (button, input, form, dialog, vs.)
├── shared/          # Cross-feature reusable (Sidebar, DataTable, PermissionGate, ...)
├── users/           # Feature-specific (UserForm, UserDetailCard, ...)
├── processes/       # Feature-specific
├── tasks/           # Feature-specific
└── admin/           # Admin-specific (AdminSidebar, PermissionMatrix, ...)
```

## shadcn/ui Usage

Primitives (`<Button>`, `<Input>`, `<Form>`, `<Dialog>`, etc.) `components/ui/` altında — shadcn CLI ile install:

```bash
pnpm --filter web exec shadcn@latest add button input form dialog
```

**Doğrudan düzenle** — shadcn pattern: component kodu senin. Theme customization `components/ui/<name>.tsx`'te.

```typescript
// components/ui/button.tsx — shadcn'dan gelen, customize edilmiş
import { cva } from 'class-variance-authority';

const buttonVariants = cva(
  'inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-md font-medium transition-colors',
  {
    variants: {
      variant: {
        default: 'bg-primary text-primary-foreground hover:bg-primary/90',
        destructive: 'bg-destructive text-destructive-foreground hover:bg-destructive/90',
        outline: 'border border-input hover:bg-accent',
        ghost: 'hover:bg-accent',
        link: 'text-primary underline-offset-4 hover:underline',
      },
      size: { default: 'h-10 px-4', sm: 'h-9 px-3', lg: 'h-11 px-8' },
    },
    defaultVariants: { variant: 'default', size: 'default' },
  }
);
```

## PermissionGate

UI-level permission filtering. Server-side enforcement zorunlu (bu sadece UX):

```typescript
// components/shared/PermissionGate.tsx
'use client';

import { usePermissions } from '@/hooks/usePermissions';
import { Permission } from '@leanmgmt/shared-types';

interface Props {
  requires: Permission | Permission[];
  mode?: 'all' | 'any';  // default 'all'
  fallback?: React.ReactNode;
  children: React.ReactNode;
}

export function PermissionGate({ 
  requires, 
  mode = 'all', 
  fallback = null, 
  children 
}: Props) {
  const permissions = usePermissions();
  const required = Array.isArray(requires) ? requires : [requires];
  
  const hasAccess = mode === 'all'
    ? required.every((p) => permissions.has(p))
    : required.some((p) => permissions.has(p));

  return hasAccess ? <>{children}</> : <>{fallback}</>;
}
```

Usage:

```typescript
<PermissionGate requires={Permission.USER_CREATE}>
  <Button onClick={() => router.push('/users/new')}>Yeni Kullanıcı</Button>
</PermissionGate>

<PermissionGate 
  requires={[Permission.AUDIT_LOG_VIEW, Permission.USER_LIST_VIEW]} 
  mode="any"
>
  <AdminMenu />
</PermissionGate>
```

Nav item'lar, action button'lar, table action'lar — permission olmayan kullanıcıya gösterme. Backend zaten reject eder ama UX cluttered olmasın.

## DataTable

Tablo için tek component. TanStack Table + shadcn:

```typescript
// components/shared/DataTable.tsx
'use client';

import { useReactTable, getCoreRowModel, flexRender, ColumnDef } from '@tanstack/react-table';

interface Props<TData> {
  data: TData[];
  columns: ColumnDef<TData>[];
  onRowClick?: (row: TData) => void;
  isLoading?: boolean;
  emptyMessage?: string;
}

export function DataTable<TData>({ 
  data, 
  columns, 
  onRowClick, 
  isLoading, 
  emptyMessage 
}: Props<TData>) {
  const table = useReactTable({
    data,
    columns,
    getCoreRowModel: getCoreRowModel(),
  });

  if (isLoading) return <TableSkeleton />;
  if (!data.length) return <EmptyState message={emptyMessage ?? 'Kayıt bulunamadı'} />;

  return (
    <div className="rounded-md border">
      <Table>
        <TableHeader>
          {table.getHeaderGroups().map((group) => (
            <TableRow key={group.id}>
              {group.headers.map((header) => (
                <TableHead key={header.id}>
                  {flexRender(header.column.columnDef.header, header.getContext())}
                </TableHead>
              ))}
            </TableRow>
          ))}
        </TableHeader>
        <TableBody>
          {table.getRowModel().rows.map((row) => (
            <TableRow 
              key={row.id}
              onClick={() => onRowClick?.(row.original)}
              className={onRowClick ? 'cursor-pointer hover:bg-muted/50' : ''}
            >
              {row.getVisibleCells().map((cell) => (
                <TableCell key={cell.id}>
                  {flexRender(cell.column.columnDef.cell, cell.getContext())}
                </TableCell>
              ))}
            </TableRow>
          ))}
        </TableBody>
      </Table>
    </div>
  );
}
```

Her list view `<DataTable>` kullanır — paralel implement yasak.

## FormLayout

Form sayfa layout'u standardize:

```typescript
// components/shared/FormLayout.tsx
interface Props {
  title: string;
  description?: string;
  breadcrumbs: Array<{ label: string; href?: string }>;
  children: React.ReactNode;
}

export function FormLayout({ title, description, breadcrumbs, children }: Props) {
  return (
    <div className="max-w-2xl mx-auto py-6 space-y-6">
      <Breadcrumb items={breadcrumbs} />
      <div>
        <h1 className="text-2xl font-semibold">{title}</h1>
        {description && (
          <p className="text-muted-foreground mt-1">{description}</p>
        )}
      </div>
      <Card>
        <CardContent className="pt-6">{children}</CardContent>
      </Card>
    </div>
  );
}
```

Usage:
```typescript
<FormLayout 
  title="Yeni Kullanıcı" 
  breadcrumbs={[
    { label: 'Kullanıcılar', href: '/users' },
    { label: 'Yeni' }
  ]}
>
  <UserForm />
</FormLayout>
```

## EmptyState

İki tür ayırt et:

```typescript
// components/shared/EmptyState.tsx
interface Props {
  icon?: React.ComponentType<{ className?: string }>;
  title: string;
  description?: string;
  action?: { label: string; onClick: () => void };
}

export function EmptyState({ icon: Icon, title, description, action }: Props) {
  return (
    <div className="flex flex-col items-center justify-center py-12 text-center">
      {Icon && <Icon className="h-12 w-12 text-muted-foreground mb-4" />}
      <h3 className="text-lg font-semibold">{title}</h3>
      {description && (
        <p className="text-muted-foreground mt-1 max-w-sm">{description}</p>
      )}
      {action && (
        <Button onClick={action.onClick} className="mt-4">
          {action.label}
        </Button>
      )}
    </div>
  );
}
```

**First-empty** vs **filter-empty** farkını koru:
```typescript
// First empty — no records yet
<EmptyState 
  icon={UserPlus}
  title="Henüz kullanıcı eklenmedi"
  description="İlk kullanıcıyı oluşturarak başlayın."
  action={{ label: 'Yeni Kullanıcı', onClick: goToNewUser }}
/>

// Filter empty — records exist but filter excluded all
<EmptyState 
  icon={Search}
  title="Filtreye uyan kullanıcı bulunamadı"
  action={{ label: 'Filtreleri temizle', onClick: clearFilters }}
/>
```

## ConfirmDialog

Destructive action'lar için:

```typescript
<ConfirmDialog
  open={open}
  onOpenChange={setOpen}
  onConfirm={() => deleteMutation.mutate(id)}
  title="Kullanıcıyı Pasifleştir"
  description="Bu işlem kullanıcının erişimini kaldıracak. İstediğiniz zaman tekrar aktifleştirebilirsiniz."
  confirmLabel="Pasifleştir"
