## Styling — Tailwind + cn() Helper

```typescript
// lib/utils.ts
import { clsx, ClassValue } from 'clsx';
import { twMerge } from 'tailwind-merge';

export function cn(...inputs: ClassValue[]) {
  return twMerge(clsx(inputs));
}
```

Usage:
```typescript
<div className={cn(
  'flex items-center gap-2',
  isActive && 'bg-primary text-primary-foreground',
  disabled && 'opacity-50 cursor-not-allowed',
  className  // allow override from parent
)} />
```

Inline style YASAK — Tailwind class kullan. Dinamik değer varsa CSS variable:

```typescript
<div 
  className="w-[var(--progress)]" 
  style={{ '--progress': `${percent}%` } as React.CSSProperties} 
/>
```

## Component Composition Rules

- Props **destructure** component tanımında, interface ayrı (implicit type'lar runtime signal)
- Default prop values interface'te `?:`, destructure'da `= default`
- Children explicit: `children: React.ReactNode`
- Forward ref gereken case'lerde `forwardRef` + `displayName`
- Compound component pattern: `<Select><SelectTrigger /><SelectContent /></Select>` — complex şeylerde yeğlenir

## Banned Patterns

- Inline CSS `style={{ ... }}` (Tailwind tercih)
- `className="..."` içinde conditional string concat (`cn()` kullan)
- `<img>` (use `next/image`)
- `<a href>` internal nav (use `<Link>`)
- Framer Motion / other animation libs MVP'de (Tailwind transitions yeter)
- Date library mixing (use `date-fns` only, luxon/moment yasak)
- Multiple table implementations (use `<DataTable>`)
- Parallel form patterns (use RHF + shadcn Form)
- Toast duplication (global `<Toaster />` root'ta, component'te tek instance)

